Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:23:01.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那麼平凡 卻那麼特別
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:05.05,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}看 若非這雙眼睛
